Converts a `Box<str>` into a `Box<[u8]>` without copying or allocating.

# Examples

```
let s = "this is a string";
let boxed_str = s.to_owned().into_boxed_str();
let boxed_bytes = boxed_str.into_boxed_bytes();
assert_eq!(*boxed_bytes, *s.as_bytes());
```
